  <data key="d2">The case-control study took place in Vietnam and found high prevalence of bed net use among children.&lt;SEP&gt;Vietnam is a country where the elimination of Aedes aegypti mosquitoes occurred through community-based mosquito control efforts.&lt;SEP&gt;Vietnam is a Southeast Asian country where this sustainable mosquito control strategy was found to be effective.&lt;SEP&gt;The pilot study for monitoring mosquito resistance was conducted in Vietnam.</data>
